    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for a cheap runabout or a handy project car? This one isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s an honest little vehicle with good value for someone who wants affordable wheels without spending a fortune. It\u2019s a solid option for a commuter, first car, or weekend fixer-upper, and with a bit of TLC it could really serve someone well. Priced to sell and ready for its next owner.",
