      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This car has the kind of honest, road-worn character you can\u2019t fake\u2014a budget-friendly ride with plenty of story left to tell. Perfect for someone who wants affordable wheels, a hands-on project, or a practical backup vehicle, it offers a chance to get into a car without stretching the wallet. There\u2019s real potential here for the right buyer who appreciates grit, utility, and the satisfaction of bringing out the best in a machine with history.",
